### Healthcare Multi-Agent Platform — Example Requests
### Use with REST Client, Postman, or curl

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@token = your-jwt-access-token

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### List registered agents
GET {{baseUrl}}/agents

### Sign up (patient)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "patient@example.com",
  "password": "securepass123",
  "full_name": "Jane Patient",
  "role": "patient"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "patient@example.com",
  "password": "securepass123"
}

### Chat — symptom triage
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "message": "I have had a mild headache for 2 days",
  "session_id": "sess-001"
}

### Chat — multi-agent (prior auth + triage)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "message": "Patient needs MRI authorization and has chest pain",
  "session_id": "sess-002"
}

### Run workflow explicitly
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflow/run
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "workflow_name": "healthcare_orchestration",
  "query": "Check drug interactions between metformin and lisinopril",
  "agents": ["medication_agent", "compliance_safety_agent"]
}

### Get workflow status
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflow/{{workflow_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Register custom agent (admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/agents/register
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "agent_id": "custom_billing_agent",
  "name": "Billing Agent",
  "display_name": "Billing Specialist",
  "domain": "billing",
  "description": "Handles billing inquiries",
  "capabilities": ["billing", "claims"],
  "tools": ["payer_rules_mcp"],
  "preferred_model": "reasoning",
  "safety_level": "standard",
  "priority": 3,
  "version": "1.0.0"
}

### Create prior authorization case
POST {{baseUrl}}/prior-auth
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "patient_id": "uuid-of-patient-profile",
  "insurer": "aetna",
  "diagnosis_codes": ["M54.5"],
  "procedure_codes": ["70553"],
  "clinical_notes": "Patient with chronic low back pain, conservative treatment failed for 6 weeks. MRI lumbar spine requested.",
  "patient_data": {
    "age": 45,
    "insurance_provider": "aetna"
  }
}

### Legacy LiteLLM chat (still available)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Hello"}]
}
